---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SOCIAL, SITE } from '../lib/config';
import '../styles/prose.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Bessi Labs is the public laboratory of Alessandro Bessi — researcher, engineer, and practitioner across computation, chess, music, drawing, and physical discipline."
>
  <article class="container container--narrow about">
    <header class="about-header">
      <p class="mono muted about-header__label">About</p>
      <h1>Bessi Labs</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Bessi Labs is the public laboratory of <a href={SOCIAL.personal} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Alessandro Bessi</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        The lab exists to make multidisciplinary serious work visible — across computation, infrastructure, chess, music, drawing, endurance, and philosophy.
      </p>

      <p>
        The two sites are related but distinct. <a href={SOCIAL.personal} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">alessandrobessi.com</a> is the canonical identity page. Bessi Labs is the living archive — the place where the work is actually happening.
      </p>

      <p>
        The goal is not to collect interests. The goal is to train perception across domains, accumulate serious work over time, and turn scattered ambition into visible form.
      </p>

      <h2>The lab</h2>

      <p>The lab is organized into seven rooms:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><a href="/rooms/the-engine">Computation</a> — infrastructure, AI, systems, programming languages</li>
        <li><a href="/rooms/the-eye">Drawing</a> — perception, form, visual discipline</li>
        <li><a href="/rooms/the-board">Chess</a> — strategy, calculation, decision-making</li>
        <li><a href="/rooms/the-ear">Music</a> — harmony, rhythm, piano, bass</li>
        <li><a href="/rooms/the-body">Training</a> — endurance, strength, adaptation</li>
        <li><a href="/rooms/the-inner-lab">Philosophy</a> — attention, identity, mastery</li>
        <li><a href="/rooms/field-notes">Field Notes</a> — fragments and observations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Links</h2>
    </div>

    <nav class="about-links" aria-label="External profiles">
      <a href={SOCIAL.personal} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="about-link">
        <span class="about-link__label">Personal site</span>
        <span class="mono muted about-link__url">alessandrobessi.com</span>
      </a>
      <a href={SOCIAL.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="about-link">
        <span class="about-link__label">GitHub</span>
        <span class="mono muted about-link__url">github.com/alessandrobessi</span>
      </a>
      <a href={SOCIAL.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="about-link">
        <span class="about-link__label">LinkedIn</span>
        <span class="mono muted about-link__url">linkedin.com/in/alessandrobessi</span>
      </a>
      <a href={SOCIAL.scholar} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="about-link">
        <span class="about-link__label">Google Scholar</span>
        <span class="mono muted about-link__url">Publications and research</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/rss.xml" class="about-link">
        <span class="about-link__label">RSS Feed</span>
        <span class="mono muted about-link__url">bessilabs.com/rss.xml</span>
      </a>
    </nav>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .about-header__label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-link {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    background-color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    transition: background-color var(--transition);
  }

  .about-link:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .about-link:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-accent-light);
  }

  .about-link__label {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .about-link__url {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-align: right;
  }
</style>
